Handling phone calls to respond to network alarms and events for proactive network monitoring. 
Managing trouble tickets, outage communications, and process escalations for internal and external customers. 
Generating, driving, and updating trouble tickets via internal ticketing system. 
Performing fault isolation, triaging, and repairing network events to ensure the health of our network. 
Working with external and internal Verizon organizations to coordinate and troubleshoot network events. 
Providing network technical assistance to external teams by communicating technical details to customer service centers, technical support organizations, and executive management teams during network events and major outages. 
Improve automation through scripting and robotics process automation (RPA) to improve team functions and efficiency. 
